targets.rawSql:
SELECT  count(email) as total
FROM Members

SELECT count(email) as 'assigned squad'
FROM Members M join SquadMembers SM on M.id = SM.memberId

SELECT count(*) as total
FROM Journeys

SELECT count(distinct J.id) as 'assigned feature'
FROM Journeys J join JourneyFeatures JF on J.id = JF.journeyId

SELECT count(*) as total
FROM Features

SELECT count(distinct F.id) as 'assigned squad'
FROM Features F join FeatureSquads FS on F.id = FS.featureId
SELECT count(*) as total FROM Sources

SELECT count(distinct S.id) as 'assigned feature'
FROM Sources S join FeatureSources FS on S.id = FS.sourceid

SELECT  J.family, count(J.journey) as journeys
from  Journeys J
group by J.family
order by journeys desc

SELECT  J.journey, count(F.feature) as features
from  Journeys J left join JourneyFeatures JF on  J.id = JF.journeyId left join Features F  on JF.featureId = F.id
group by J.journey
order by features desc

SELECT  F.feature, count(J.Journey) as journeys
from Features F left join JourneyFeatures JF on JF.featureId = F.id left join Journeys J on J.id = JF.journeyId
group by F.feature
order by journeys desc

SELECT  J.family, J.avaSlo, J.expSlo, J.latSlo, J.journey, F.feature, S.source
FROM Journeys J 
join JourneyFeatures JF on J.id = JF.journeyId
join Features F on JF.featureId = F.id
join FeatureSources FS on F.id = FS.featureId
join Sources S on FS.sourceId = S.id

SELECT  S.squad, count(F.feature) as features
from  Squads S left join FeatureSquads FS on  FS.squadId = S.id left join Features F on F.id = FS.featureId
group by S.squad
order by features desc

SELECT  F.feature, count(S.source) as sources
from Features F left join FeatureSources FS on F.id = FS.featureId left join Sources S on FS.sourceId = S.id
group by F.feature
order by sources desc

SELECT  F.feature, S.squad
from Features F left join FeatureSquads FS on F.id = FS.featureId left join Squads S on FS.squadId = S.id

SELECT  S.source, F.feature
from  Sources S left join FeatureSources FS on   FS.sourceId = S.id left join Features F on F.id = FS.featureId
